<subSubSection id="02C66578FFFCFFBDFC959F386ABF7916" pageId="17" pageNumber="31" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFFCFFBDFC959F386D8E7E94" blockId="17.[831,1437,892,1143]" pageId="17" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFFCFFBDFC959F386ABD7EF5" bold="true" box="[831,944,892,916]" pageId="17" pageNumber="31">Remarks:</emphasis>
It is characterized by very elongate test usually slightly curved. The chambers are distinct, earlier chambers are not inflated but the later chambers become increasingly inflated as added.
</paragraph>
